2 (a) operational instructions, if any;
3 (b) safety guidelines for the ride, if any;
4 (c) restrictions on the use of the amusement ride, if any;
5 (d) behavior or activities that are prohibited, if any; and
6 (e) the following statement: "State law requires riders and passengers to obey all warnings and
