22 Section 6. Section 27-1-745, MCA, is amended to read:
23 "27-1-745. Injury reports and investigations. (1) (a) A passenger who is injured on or by an
24 amusement ride is encouraged to report the injury to the operator before leaving the amusement ride premises.
25 The passenger shall, if possible, not later than 6 months after the injury, report the injury to the operator or to
26 the owner of the premises where the amusement ride was located at the time of the injury. The report must
27 include:
28 (i) the passenger's name, address, and telephone number;
